<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>


<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Statistical Tests</Bold> combo box includes a list of statistical functions.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Perform Test</Bold> button performs the selected test.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Sample1 Mean</Bold> slider sets the mean for the first series.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Sample1 Variance</Bold> slider sets the variance for the first series.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Sample2 Mean</Bold> slider sets the mean for the second series.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Sample2 Variance</Bold> slider sets the variance for the second series.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>


</List>
